32473510", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 26}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "「双刃剑」武器本身并不会容易伤到使用者，为什么要用「双刃剑」来说事物的两面性？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "「双刃剑」作为武器是很正常的剑的样式，在中国古代刀剑区分的语境中，剑一定是双刃的，双刃作为武器也并不是一个失败的设计。 那么，为什么在比喻中，「双刃剑」被视为是有优势也有劣势，刃的两面被视为一面伤对方，一面伤自己呢？「双刃剑」比喻中，本体是否并不具有喻体所蕴含的性质？ 查证了一下英文词典，double-edged sword 也确实被用来表示和中文「双刃剑」近似的语义。所以中间肯定不是、至少不是只有文化差异或翻译错误在起作用。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac14b756da7b426cc3b1afdb833750c2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/632473510"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iz4TN2fL25o1rEAMaCTEwMjgyODMxNCDW55urBjAAODdAJHIJNjMyNDczNTEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "37_1702051845.611717", "card_id": "Q_607006033", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 295}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "什么是决策的本质？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7ac4d14c2364b69911b12c4ce220ffaa_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/607006033"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iz4TN2fL25o1rEAMaCDk3MTcwNjU5IOL6sKQGMAA4uQRAJXIJNjA3MDA2MDMzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1702051845.611910", "card_id": "Q_632472692", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 78}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年，职场人的心态都发生了哪些变化？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-de3f62c81eba4fc89f93785f3ab51d25.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "lin